Package: bwcopyeditor
Type: Package
Title: Bellwether Copyeditor - LLM-Powered Copyediting Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A tool that uses OpenAI's LLM models to copyedit deliverable
    drafts according to project context and Bellwether style conventions.
    Preserves page numbers and returns structured output that can be
    coerced to a table or CSV.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    pdftools,
    stringr,
    officer
Suggests:
    testthat
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
